{
  "texts": [
    "We report the best result for Distill-step-by-step by leveraging different teacher models.",
    "For the choice of LLMs, we use FLAN-T5 [11] small (80M), base (250M), and large (780M) as the student, and FLAN-T5 xlarge (3B) and LLaMA 2-chat [61] (7B) as teachers.",
    "Experiments are conducted on four NVIDIA H100 Tensor Core GPUs.",
    "Performance ComparisonComparison to Baselines Methods.",
    "We conducted a thorough evaluation of our method, TinyLLM, across six diverse datasets spanning two distinct reasoning tasks: commonsense reasoning and biomedical reasoning."
  ]
}